nemo-crypt (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add anonymous recipient encryption option (--throw-keyids)
  * Add key selection dialog for anonymous encrypted files
  * Add comprehensive debug logging system (NEMO_CRYPT_DEBUG)
  * Extract shared GPG key listing functions to gpg-common.sh
  * Improve error handling and validation throughout
  * Fix shell scripting vulnerabilities in key parsing
  * Disable anonymous checkbox appropriately in symmetric mode
  * Add better error messages for decryption failures

 -- John Crouch <github@ko4dfo.com>  Sun, 15 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000

nemo-crypt (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * GPG encryption/decryption integration for Nemo file manager
  * Support for symmetric and asymmetric encryption
  * Digital signature verification
  * Multi-file packaging support (zip, tar.gz, tar.bz2)
  * GTK3 encryption settings dialog
  * Comprehensive error handling and validation
  * Security improvements: path traversal protection, cleanup traps

 -- John Crouch <github@ko4dfo.com>  Sat, 14 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000
